{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be clean and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #C62828; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #E0E0E0; /* Light Grey */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #D32F2F; /* Slightly darker red */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        /* Font Awesome integration (optional, for icons) */\n        @import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Apex Financial Consulting</h1>\n        <p>Navigating Your Financial Future with Expertise and Clarity</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At Apex Financial Consulting, we are dedicated to providing strategic financial guidance to individuals and businesses. Our team of seasoned professionals leverages deep industry knowledge and a client-centric approach to help you achieve your financial goals. We believe in transparency, integrity, and building long-term partnerships.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Investment Strategy</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored investment plans designed to maximize returns and manage risk.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-piggy-bank\"></i>\n                    <h3>Retirement Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Secure your future with comprehensive retirement savings and income strategies.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h3>Business Financials</h3>\n                    <p>Expert advice on cash flow management, funding, and growth for your business.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                    <p>Protect your assets and mitigate financial risks with our proactive solutions.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ready to take control of your financial future? Contact us today for a free initial consultation.</p>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"window.location.href='mailto:info@apexfinancial.com';\">Contact Us</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}